<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{exterior police car night}
<A>__{the ride progresses in silence. hansen and tandy in the front seat. maurice's head is pressed against the back seat window. his eyes begin to shut slightly as sleep overcomes him. the car goes over a bump. maurice jars awake. he glances out the window to see a highway sign swish by in the headlights. 'route 80 east'. east? maurice looks around quickly at the passing scenery.}
<C>__{maurice}
<D>__{where are you taking me?}
